VLLO s editor UI has been renewed! We try to make VLLO more user centered and easy to use. Check out the new VLLO right now. 1. It went from 3 tracks to 4 tracks. New features are coming soon! 2. The positions of the Add Media and Storyboard buttons have been changed for intuitive use of the buttons. 3. We understand that you use the Undo and Redo buttons very often. From now on you can use these buttons on any edit screen. 4. Frame by frame editing just got easier. Edit your video in more detail frame by frame. VLLO team is always doing our best to provide a comfortable editing experience for users. Please look forward to VLLO updates!
